#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:4
msgid "Relative Paths"
msgstr "相对路径"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:6
msgid ""
"Many blend-files reference external images or other linked blend-files. A path tells "
"Blender where to look for these files. If the external files are moved, the blend-file "
"that references them will not look right."
msgstr ""
"很多Blend文件引用了外部图像或关联的Blend文件。路径告诉Blender在哪里查找这些文件。如果外部"
"文件已被移动，引用他们的Blend文件也会出错。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:10
msgid ""
"When you specify one of these external files, the default option is to make the path "
"relative. Blender stores a partial path evaluated relative to the directory location of "
"the referencing blend-file. This choice helps when you need to reorganize folders or "
"move your files."
msgstr ""
"当用户指定其中一个外部文件时，默认选项是使用相对路径。Blender存储相对当前文件所在目录的部"
"分路径。这在用户需要重新组织文件夹或移动文件时很有帮助。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:14
msgid ""
"With a relative path, you can move the blend-file to a new location provided the "
"externally linked files are moved along with it. For example, you could send someone a "
"folder that contains a blend-file and a sub-folder of external images that it references."
msgstr ""
"使用相对路径，在外部关联文件跟着一起移动时，用户可将该Blend文件移到一个新位置。例如，用户"
"可以发送一个包含blend文件的文件夹，并将引用的外部图片放在其子文件夹下。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:19
msgid ""
"When relative paths are supported, the File Browser provides a *Relative Path* check "
"box, when entering the path into a text field, use a double slash prefix (``//``) to "
"make it so."
msgstr ""
"在支持相对路径的情形下，文件浏览器会提供一个 *相对路径* 的复选框，输入文件路径时，使用双"
"斜杠(``//``) 代替。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:22
msgid ""
"Relative paths are the default but this can be changed in the :doc:`File </preferences/"
"file>` tab of the User Preferences Editor."
msgstr ""
"默认使用相对路径，但可以在用户设置的 :doc:`文件 </preferences/file>` 选项卡中更改。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:28
msgid ""
"You cannot enter relative paths into a new *untitled* blend-file. Save it before linking "
"to external files."
msgstr "对于新建的 *untitled* blend文件不能输入相对路径。在关联外部文件前先进行保存。"

#: ../../manual/data_system/files/relative_paths.rst:33
msgid ""
"If it is necessary to relocate a blend-file relative to its linked resources, use "
"Blender's File :doc:`Save As </data_system/files/save>` function which has an option to "
"*Remap Relative* file links."
msgstr ""
"如果需要重新定位blend关联的源文件的相对位置，可以使用 :doc:`另存为</data_system/files/"
"save>` 功能，勾选 *更新相对路径* 选项。"
